    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>RSACountdown</strong>: a logical-qubits slider that maps
      RSA key size against estimated qubit requirements
      (<code>2·key_size + overhead</code>), with markers for "today",
      current vendor roadmaps, and the rough "break RSA-2048"
